exceptions.exn: In environment p, q1, q2 : nat H : p div q1 H0 : p div q1 + q2 Unable to unify "exists p : nat, q1 + ?M1410 = p * ?M1408" with "exists p0 : nat, q2 = p0 * p".

original: intros q2 q1 p H1 H2. apply divides_plus with (q1:=q1); auto.
